| `delete_all_sessions()` + `DeleteAllResult` | `backend/src/runtime/session.rs` | ✅ Implemented | Lines 88-127: deletes all `.jsonl` files, creates new session, returns `DeleteAllResult { deleted_count, new_session_id }` |
| DELETE `/api/forge/chats/sessions/all` route | `backend/src/forge/mod.rs` | ✅ Implemented | Route registered: `.route("/api/forge/chats/sessions", get(handlers::list_forge_sessions).delete(handlers::delete_all_forge_sessions))` |
| `deleteAllSessions()` composable | `frontend/src/composables/useSessions.ts` | ✅ Implemented | Lines 55-87: calls `DELETE ${API_BASE}/sessions/all`, updates `_sessionList`, returns `{ deletedCount, newSessionId, session }` |
| Delete-all button in ChatsView | `frontend/src/views/ChatsView.vue` | ✅ Implemented | Line 12: `<button class="sidebar-delete-all-btn">` with Trash2 icon, `v-if="sessionList.length > 0"` |
| `confirmDeleteAll()` handler | `frontend/src/views/ChatsView.vue` | ✅ Implemented | Uses `confirm(t('chat.confirmDeleteAll'))` + calls `deleteAllSessions()` |
| `hasSessions` computed | `frontend/src/composables/useSessions.ts` | ✅ Implemented | Returns `_sessionList.value.length > 0` |
